    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package is accepted for submission to the regulatory dossier as a complete documentation artifact under the Minimal profile. The assessment documents that all 13 credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 requirements; 7 factors were formally assessed and 6 were flagged as epistemic gaps. The achieved levels fall below required levels across all assessed factors, consistent with the Not Accepted device-level decision recorded in the COU. The package satisfies the documentation completeness requirements referenced in the project requirements specification and is accepted as an accurate record of the current model credibility status. Further V&V activities are required before the model can support a positive regulatory submission.",
